            "text": "The state hardware-ban map is being redrawn — with dates attached",
            "wrap": true,
            "spacing": "Small"
          },
          {
            "type": "TextBlock",
            "text": "New Jersey’s own State Police now tell dealers the Third Circuit ruling takes effect July 31 — a week after Virginia’s injunction went live, and the same week a gun-rights coalition moved to block Maryland’s Glock ban before it can start.",
